column10:
NBA 2K might possibly be the epitome of regurgitated garbagel; the poster boy if you will. I've never seen a game that has SUCH piss poor AI that it ruins the game but it does. Please, If you have any sense of reason DO NOT GET THIS GAME. It is a nightmare. It almost literally doesn't change from year to year. It has a TERRIBLE simulation "basletball simulation" my a$$. It is beyond garbage, THE ONLY Reason this is a basketball game is because you play the game of basketball. In no way does it accurately recreate a thing. Literally the worst game i have ever played. It is the most money hungry franchise I've ever seen in gaming. It's a god damn shame that NBA Live was canceled because NBA 2K is TRASH.


TLDR;
DO NOT BUY THIS GAME FOR ANYTHING OVER FREE.
